<mixer template="gw.tmpl">
<mixertitle>Installation Feedback </mixertitle>

<p>
    We ask you to inform us when you download and install
    <mixer var="GAP"/>. Please write a brief email letter to the address
    <mixer person="GAP" data="email_link"/>
    informing us about
</p>
<ul>
   <li>
    your name, e-mail address and institution, 
   </li>   
   <li>
   the type of installation (used operating system and computer(s)),
   </li>
   <li>
   the number of people who will use this installation,
   </li>
   <li>
   earlier versions of GAP installed by you, if any,
   </li>
   <li>
   your area of (mathematical) interest that led you to the installation of
   <mixer var="GAP"/>,
   </li>
   <li>
   possibly remarks and suggestions concerning the installation of
   <mixer var="GAP"/>.
   </li>
</ul>      
   
  
</mixer>

